{"tid":2429742,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度有黃嘅Pizza鋪？","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T01:02:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0484ce969c289675e4b515e6e9c8dd6d0647cce7","tid":2429742,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到<br />\nPizza box 喺cctvb長期賣廣告<br />\nPHD Pizza Hut 係怡和<br />\n咁仲有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\npizzabox本身唔係藍店，但因為長期喺tvb賣廣告自動申請咗藍店稱號，呢啲真係PR界傻仔，俾曬好牌都唔識上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">🚫 Pizza-BOX 🚫</span></span></strong><br />\n點擊下面派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/350923911654846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F350923911654846&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=ccd474a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/350923911654846</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMi4NFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMi4NFb.jpg&h=7a241bfb&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<blockquote>糾正及道歉聲明：最近小編指責怡和旗下嘅PHD薄餅博士喺TVB賣廣告，小編其實係想指Pizza-Box(與怡和無關)而唔係PHD。為各位帶嚟誤會，小編感到非常抱歉😢 <br />\n<br />\n目前，Pizza-BOX係唯一一間，亦係長期喺TVB賣廣告嘅連鎖薄餅店(以2020年起計算)。相反，PHD同Pizza Hut仍然可以Keep住無喺TVB落廣告。<br />\n<br />\n雖然怡和係藍，我哋大可以唔出澄清，不過我認為做得page就有責任提供正確資訊畀大家，所以都要還返個公道畀PHD，資訊就提供咗畀大家，大家自己決定點做喇。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0c37a42218d8c0cef1afb5a98cbcc3efa7eb61bd","tid":2429742,"uid":385687,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"jacomax 同 mother of pizzas都又黃又正"},{"pid":"bade6722e63c9fa823bd3a930cc6fc3618d4f750","tid":2429742,"uid":252541,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"Piccolo Pizzeria &amp; Bar<br />\n2824 3000<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/DSM2B8mE3vHK6iep6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FDSM2B8mE3vHK6iep6&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=a3d281e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/DSM2B8mE3vHK6iep6</a>"},{"pid":"692064492bd254f049800a437857a550d92cfc26","tid":2429742,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c37a42218d8c0cef1afb5a98cbcc3efa7eb61bd","tid":2429742,"uid":385687,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"jacomax 同 mother of pizzas都又黃又正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"媽打要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dbd525adade24b21b77a67ede723048934cecf","tid":2429742,"uid":60924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"jacomax. 外賣 都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f4a26f3e3e3234806b87c9ea8d026a6e11b4f9","tid":2429742,"uid":392196,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"Pizza Hut"},{"pid":"3ec2dccd4a728d3605d68be72320f18b07ebbd3e","tid":2429742,"uid":261505,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"Pizzahut logo勁黃"},{"pid":"db6f3351b5d8d790ecdfeaadf72a5b4d119469aa","tid":2429742,"uid":46072,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n新西有Canadian pizza<br />\n不過唔係好知背景"},{"pid":"094d04f12df370b8